{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"轻轻的菲","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-22","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEoibPTIXiabwRaYPAu409t7cxXcX1SyyoY3VC9Sj2zAEURtVAsnKu8fbVia26ic5K1h8PMtQ1bg1QdvA/0","content":"不可信的，各种养生信息，前小道偏方等。以及，天气预报哈哈。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1543,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487763823000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"我爱喝茶水","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjJU1qLRSMWg0RYibvZEGaRKIZnmBqPWvsoXS1VeKibTMVSY2CuSvEVKNkAPVUqaCelUsqEbENvZl0D/0","content":"比如一些保健品的功效，可治百病；无证行医的假专家等不可靠。\n政府部门发布的信息相对可靠。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1179,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487589611000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"喃喃","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKsiaBXqlAJsMAVeMK7vBibQzub1OMVJ9uZMq9ibiba9ZdViaaVXAEnl9OJZdrQLPMyvakxibeOEWqP6jjwxYsfqL7418/0","content":"可信信息：官方（人民网、新浪网）发布的信息，知乎中的行家解说，知名医院医生的微博\n不可信的信息：朋友圈传播的类似不转发就怎样的信息，说法太过绝对无官方背景的科普，百度看病","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1107,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487567424000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Virgo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKVSJ7zgg19tZBDs4xHFCJJG1pzr4tuicg7SbMfKBToWk4WbaGniaZTnQRWYpH7DRZiaNwm0Yicr9zXn9VkAFWia9nW6/0","content":"因为家里老人一般多看养生这些东西，那就这方面来总结一下。\n\n1）我崇尚的观念是授人鱼不如授人以渔——与其告诉他们哪些可信不可信，不如告诉他们如何去区分，那要做到如下几点\n\n1. 首先辨别信息来源的渠道\n\n2. 其次辨别信息质量—学会区分事实和观点（但是老人的难点在于不知道哪些是健身养生的事实）\n\n3. 最后要学会因地制宜—适合自己的才是最好的\n\n\n2）如果做不到授人以渔，那就按照以下几个判断标准\n\n1.你看到的信息是否有违常识\n\n2.自己多总结一些可靠渠道直接推荐给家里老人\n\n3.当看到老人误信信息时可以晓之以理动之以情。\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":976,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487470846000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"金小金","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6ibkOl3cs3WZ1N8B16l2BYCT8iaEiaFibaaNX5FewClYS6RCMfI1aj1ggiaZvP53j0TBl2K7MAJQsjTnrQ/0","content":"以养生类为例：\n不可信的是一些没有科学依据的偏方、土方，或者是一些被过份鼓吹的补品类食物\n可信的是一些被科学证实并业是多数人实践验证的东西\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":794,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487308793000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Claudia\uD83C\uDF88孙雪","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQHEGlNicG6ucZIjY65zAdPsmz39B6Cc3Eib47zwsibAicbBofwLZ9giaYlG5FlJSSKovICibSd49qaEFyI/0","content":"权威可信的：\n1. 不掺杂主观偏向的客观新闻报道；\n2. 相关领域专家的建议，并且该专家在此问题上没有利益牵涉其中，如权威养生专家提出的养生建议；\n3. 很多人亲身试验有效，并且反面例子较少的事情，比如10个人里面7个人都说锦绣山值得一去，那么很有可能是真的。\n\n不可信的：\n1. 鸡汤文，没有实质方法论和理论来源；\n2. 众口相传的各种骗局，如出现闻一口就吐露银行卡密码的迷药，没有证据和专家证实；\n3. 养生偏方，来源不明，权威性存疑。\n4. 微商，以个例做证据，且利益出发点存疑，可靠性较低。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":787,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487300975000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"毛豆花生、疙瘩汤","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCicvScoho5aByfuZC6mCMRVE3ajsF1LjtsTEcqN95Qdw4k3HWoOs9cVgeBOcJoWrz0DS0g3h85Rdg/0","content":"主流大媒体对时事新闻的事实报道可信，基于图片、文字等为事实依据的自媒体推文可信。没有相关事实依据的言论和说法不可信。\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":1,"submitId":681,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486968415000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"程然","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibeXpgwkiaTloWbvWZibHU3ulLlIhhE6iaIiazJaXkXaYkTTbdwvhdOM7cvxOoQpCxud7DYns8icjZDZ7w/0","content":"1、看证据的真实性\n1)发布者是否是发布内容相关的官方机构？\n2)发布者是否在发布内容方面是权威人物？\n3)发布者是否和发布内容利益相关方？\n2、看行文逻辑漏洞\n1）是否以偏概全\n2）是否错误述诸\n3）是否滑坡谬误\n4）是否人身攻击\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":677,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486965415000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"貓宁姜","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6agqPwVy4opWYcSWZaVneib0f1rTHkIZ5qhFcGKRAEsbjrQibqJfRIenSXe22uFMgHC2O99xEGECEh6e11rMFfjO9/0","content":"哪些可信：有明确标明参考资料的。\n\n\n\n哪些不可信：做广告的","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":608,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486704788000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Juvae","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoO92kqn9zYibHA0icSRJB8q67kFhVGDz9UJ3YIOsTr2zWFh6iaIycONL49U7HgkfokASzcIeLjQq9dO/0","content":"家里老人的信息来源主要是电视、广播、网络上的专家讲座的内容和新闻播报内容。\n足够权威可信的：经确认的官方发布的新闻等。\n\n不可信的：缺乏逻辑的鸡汤文章、没有科学依据的专家言论。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":487,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486298820000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"黄国宏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-24","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WUxgnmxEpgc8X4bzchak2q91qcWtB5kgsZyejpC6ia59CCIWMMG6br8w5EiccYv71UZ1L8Jxey1fU6xNu7OcaNVp/0","content":"我写的是关于老人上网买理财产品的安全分析<img src=\"http://www.iqycamp.com/images/application/application-20170124171441-rxyw7efj1-381.png\" style=\"max-width:90%\"/>","voteCount":2,"commentCount":0,"submitId":381,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1485244571000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":["http://www.iqycamp.com/images/application/application-20170124171441-rxyw7efj1-381.png"]},{"title":null,"userName":"Ryan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6aEeXiaMnZEMehcLPtcMFnveQrtsZpicL7063KxCsXqV5jiaczYbmwOBo3LrEF2nPiarw2cg9eXlUkNndKCjc58jN6l/0","content":"1、看网站，如果是权威网站，相对可信度就比较高。如果是乱七八糟的网站，可信度就不高，极有可能是为了点击率而瞎写的文章。\n2、看写文章的人。如果是某行业的知名人物，专栏作家等等，这些人写出来的文章，可信度就比较高。\n3、看文章内容。引据的事实居多，可信度就高。大多数再说自己的观点，可信度就低。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":308,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484826421000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"慕容依","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEKib0YjdFPpaJa7Hqat2Ug4a50kNcl5eqgcqTpwYCZcgxIV32qK9T7Tg99uDx5bvVoZIE1PgggJm6g/0","content":"那些由个案、特例、用类比方法推论出来的一般道理不太可信。\n哪些可信，也说不太好，圈圈这样的比较可信。\n我做这个题目没有思路，能不能给点提示123","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":41,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484558347000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
